jadi tampan habis ini...,</font>

889
01:15:41,684 --> 01:15:43,084
<font color="yellow">...tapi nanti...</font>

890
01:15:43,244 --> 01:15:46,314
<font color="yellow">...aku tidak berharga dan tak ada
gunanya lagi. Aku jadi khawatir.</font>

891
01:15:46,614 --> 01:15:49,214
<font color="yellow">Jadi aku sudah menuliskan
kontrak.</font>

892
01:15:51,844 --> 01:15:55,684
<font color="yellow"><i>[Ji Eun Tak, Pengantin Goblin: Pemohon
Goblin Ahjussi: Penyetuju]</i></font>

893
01:15:59,344 --> 01:16:02,384
<font color="yellow">Aku memberikan semua makanan itu biar
kau belajar, bukan menulis ini.</font>

894
01:16:02,584 --> 01:16:05,014
<font color="yellow">Kau juga harus membaca kalimat terakhirnya.</font>

895
01:16:07,244 --> 01:16:09,184
<font color="yellow"><i>Pada hari salju pertama
turun tiap tahun...</i></font>

896
01:16:09,184 --> 01:16:10,914
<font color="yellow"><i>...si Penyetuju harus
mengabulkan permintaan si Pemohon.</i></font>

897
01:16:10,914 --> 01:16:13,344
<font color="yellow"><i>Karena si Pemohon akan
menunggu si Sang Penyetuju.</i></font>

898
01:16:13,544 --> 01:16:14,614
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau sungguh akan mati?</i></font>

899
01:16:17,214 --> 01:16:18,214
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

900
01:16:19,614 --> 01:16:20,844
<font color="yellow">Sebelum salju pertama turun.</font>

901
01:16:22,114 --> 01:16:24,444
<font color="yellow">Kenapa salju pertama?</font>

902
01:16:27,084 --> 01:16:29,214
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak ingin merusak
hari salju pertamanya.</font>

903
01:16:32,344 --> 01:16:33,814
<font color="yellow">Apa karena ini kau menanyakan namaku?</font>

904
01:16:34,514 --> 01:16:35,514
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

905
01:16:36,084 --> 01:16:37,714
<font color="yellow">Aku memang ingin tahu saja.</font>

906
01:16:38,444 --> 01:16:40,414
<font color="yellow">Namamu cocok dengan dirimu.</font>

907
01:16:45,744 --> 01:16:48,344
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu maksudku, 'kan?</font>

908
01:16:53,654 --> 01:16:55,414
<font color="yellow"><i>[Tanda Tangan: Kim Shin]</i></font>

909
01:16:58,284 --> 01:16:59,384
<font color="yellow">Ini 'kan maksudmu?</font>

910
01:16:59,914 --> 01:17:01,284
<font color="yellow">Kau bisa tahu darimana?</font>

911
01:17:01,714 --> 01:17:03,314
<font color="yellow">Padahal biasanya sulit
orang langsung tandatangan kontrak.</font>

912
01:17:11,214 --> 01:17:12,214
<font color="yellow">Daebak.</font>

913
01:17:16,214 --> 01:17:17,314
<font color="yellow">Turun salju.</font>

914
01:17:19,784 --> 01:17:21,314
<font color="yellow">Ini salju pertama, Ahjussi.</font>

915
01:17:21,714 --> 01:17:23,944
<font color="yellow">Kenapa sudah turun salju?</font>

916
01:17:24,654 --> 01:17:26,284
<font color="yellow">Keren sekali.</font>

917
01:17:27,684 --> 01:17:30,914
<font color="yellow">Aku suka karena suasananya indah,
tapi bunganya pasti kedinginan.</font>

918
01:17:31,844 --> 01:17:32,844
<font color="yellow">Ya, 'kan?</font>

919
01:17:33,214 --> 01:17:36,014
<font color="yellow">Kita sekarang sedang melihat
salju pertama yang turun lebih awal.</font>

920
01:17:38,284 --> 01:17:39,654
<font color="yellow">Ahjussi yang melakukannya, 'kan?</font>

921
01:17:39,654 --> 01:17:41,944
<font color="yellow">Kau ingin aku menarik pedangnya
waktu turun salju.</font>

922
01:17:44,514 --> 01:17:46,384
<font color="yellow">Maaf karena sikapku yang egois
selama ini...,</font>

923
01:17:47,284 --> 01:17:49,484
<font color="yellow">...tapi sikapku begitu
karena aku ingin diingat.</font>

924
01:17:55,244 --> 01:17:56,914
<font color="yellow">Sampai kapan kita berlama-lama
dan menikmati salju ini?</font>

925
01:17:56,914 --> 01:17:58,584
<font color="yellow">Kita harus buru-buru, dan
membuat Ahjussi jadi tampan.</font>

926
01:18:01,844 --> 01:18:02,914
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, sekarang.</font>

927
01:18:05,814 --> 01:18:09,244
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Sekarang waktunya
membuatmu tampan.</font>

928
01:18:09,914 --> 01:18:11,544
<font color="yellow">Ada kata-kata terakhir?</font>

929
01:18:14,014 --> 01:18:15,984
<font color="yellow">Setiap saat aku menghabiskan
waktu bersamamu itu...</font>

930
01:18:17,014 --> 01:18:18,154
<font color="yellow">...waktu yang bersinar.</font>

931
01:18:22,544 --> 01:18:23,884
<font color="yellow">Saat cuaca sedang bagus...,</font>

932
01:18:26,844 --> 01:18:28,344
<font color="yellow">...saat cuaca sedang tidak bagus...,</font>

933
01:18:31,444 --> 01:18:32,944
<font color="yellow">...dan saat cuaca yang cukup bagus...</font>

934
01:18:37,314 --> 01:18:38,784
<font color="yellow">...aku mencintai semua
saat-saat itu.</font>

935
01:18:40,444 --> 01:18:41,444
<font color="yellow">Juga...,</font>

936
01:18:43,014 --> 01:18:44,444
<font color="yellow">...apapun yang terjadi...,</font>

937
01:18:47,944 --> 01:18:49,244
<font color="yellow">...itu bukanlah kesalahanmu.</font>

938
01:18:50,344 --> 01:18:51,844
<font color="yellow">Ahjussi, apa mungkin kau...</font>

939
01:18:56,084 --> 01:18:58,514
<font color="yellow">...akan berubah jadi sapu terbang?</font>

940
01:19:00,544 --> 01:19:01,814
<font color="yellow">Itu tidak akan terjadi.</font>

941
01:19:03,684 --> 01:19:04,684
<font color="yellow">Syukurlah.</font>

942
01:19:05,744 --> 01:19:07,244
<font color="yellow">Aku mulai menariknya sekarang, ya.</font>

943
01:19:40,284 --> 01:19:42,984
<font color="yellow">Kenapa aku tidak bisa memegangnya?</font>

944
01:19:43,344 --> 01:19:45,284
<font color="yellow">Aku bisa melihatnya, tapi aku tidak
bisa memegangnya.</font>

945
01:19:48,614 --> 01:19:50,514
<font color="yellow">Apa tanganmu sudah cukup kuat?</font>

946
01:19:52,014 --> 01:19:53,814
<font color="yellow">Baik, biar kucoba lagi.</font>

947
01:20:10,314 --> 01:20:13,284
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang sebelumnya kalau
apapun yang terjadi...</font>

948
01:20:13,284 --> 01:20:15,084
<font color="yellow">...itu bukan kesalahanku...,</font>

949
01:20:15,514 --> 01:20:17,844
<font color="yellow">...jadi jangan tarik perkataan itu lagi./
Hei.</font>

950
01:20:18,244 --> 01:20:21,414
<font color="yellow">Mana bisa pengantin goblin.../
Kubilang, jangan tarik perkataanmu.</font>

951
01:20:21,414 --> 01:20:23,114
<font color="yellow">Jangan bergerak kau.</font>

952
01:20:23,114 --> 01:20:24,544
<font color="yellow">Aku malah yang jauh lebih
kaget dari kau.</font>

953
01:20:24,544 --> 01:20:26,484
<font color="yellow">Aku masih berdiri disini.
Mana bisa aku bergerak lagi?</font>

954
01:20:26,484 --> 01:20:28,014
<font color="yellow">Mana kesepakatan yang kau tulis itu?
Biar kubakar itu.</font>

955
01:20:28,014 --> 01:20:29,014
<font color="yellow">Tunggu.</font>

956
01:20:33,384 --> 01:20:36,014
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu apa itu. Pasti.
Aku mengerti sekarang.</font>

957
01:20:36,444 --> 01:20:38,444
<font color="yellow">Apa itu?/
Pangeran terkutuk.</font>

958
01:20:38,444 --> 01:20:39,884
<font color="yellow">Pangeran, yang dalam cerita dongeng itu?</font>

959
01:20:39,884 --> 01:20:41,014
<font color="yellow">Terus apa maksudmu?</font>

960
01:20:43,214 --> 01:20:44,344
<font color="yellow">Sebuah ciuman.</font>

961
01:21:00,966 --> 01:21:14,681
<font color="yellow">Indonesian Subtitle by <i><b><font color=#ffff80>Artha Regina</font></b></i></font>

962
01:21:26,914 --> 01:21:29,844
<font color="yellow"><i>[Goblin]</i></font>

963
01:21:30,784 --> 01:21:33,444
<font color="yellow"><i>Pokoknya, aku mencoba memegang pedangnya.</i></font>

964
01:21:34,184 --> 01:21:37,414
<font color="yellow"><i>Tapi, aku tidak bisa menyentuhnya
meskipun aku bisa melihatnya.</i></font>

965
01:21:37,484 --> 01:21:39,084
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia hidup lagi.</i></font>

966
01:21:39,084 --> 01:21:41,514
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia bukan pengantin goblin.
Aku akan mengusirnya.</i></font>

967
01:21:42,014 --> 01:21:43,984
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa kau perlu kartu nama?/
Aku cuma ingin saja.</i></font>

968
01:21:43,984 --> 01:21:46,014
<font color="yellow"><i>Bukannya ini nomor teleponnya Kim Woo Bin?</i></font>

969
01:21:46,014 --> 01:21:48,614
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku belum punya kartu nama./
Terus mau kau apa?</i></font>

970
01:21:48,614 --> 01:21:50,944
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa yang kau suka, Woo Bin?/
Kau, Sunny.</i></font>

971
01:21:50,944 --> 01:21:53,744
<font color="yellow"><i>Itu ciuman pertamaku, tentu saja.</i></font>

972
01:21:56,344 --> 01:21:57,344
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau tak apa?</i></font>

973
01:21:57,414 --> 01:21:59,514
<font color="yellow"><i>Tae Hee Oppa?</i></font>

974
01:22:01,914 --> 01:22:03,844
<font color="yellow"><i>Siapa di sini yang namanya Tae Hee? Keluar.</i></font>

975
01:22:03,844 --> 01:22:04,844
<font color="yellow"><i>Siapa kau?</i></font>

